    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">My Experience: The Cosmetics Brand That Lost 64% of Sales to Hidden Ingredients</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">September 2024 | Los Angeles, CA | Real cosmetics brand case study</p>

      <div class="bg-pink-50 border-[3px] border-pink-200 p-6 mb-6">
